snippet: Bae Sang-moon of South Korea made seven birdies on his way to a six-under-par 66 and a share of the lead with Andres Gonzalez at the Frys.com Open in Napa, Calif.
abstract: Bae Sang-moon of South Korea shares lead with Andres Gonzalez at the Frys.com Open in Napa, Calif; other golf news noted.
